metadata.name: Rectangular Serenity
metadata.description: "Rectangular Serenity" celebrates the beauty found in basic rectangles, hand-drawn with imperfect lines and raw charm. Embodied in minimalism, this artwork invites you to experience the tranquility of rectangles. Admire their stability and versatile forms, presented in the minimalist color palette of #EF1540 (Red) and #CDCBCE (Cool Grey), in ultra-high resolution (8192_8192). Discover the fact that rectangles have been cherished throughout history for their stability and versatility.
